APPRENTICE:

        During play, press and hold 'DEL' and 'F3' for 50 guys and all the
        extras.

        On the title screen, press 'TAB' to go to the password screen.  Now
        type any of the following level codes:  "WIZARD", "GUILD", "SPELLS",
        "ARCANE", "DRUID", and "FAERIE".

        If this doesn't work, then press tab after the first title screen.
